  "description": "<i>Letterman</i> is a 1-2 player hangman game for the 8-bit Atari computer.<br><br>The player must try to solve a word by filling in the blanks before the apple sitting atop a person's head is hit with an arrow.  Players can chose a random word or can use their own words.  Every incorrect answer causes the arrow to approach closer.  Players can choose from 3 different levels of difficulty, and can play with or without hints.  There is an option for a time limit to games.  ",
